ZH: 他赶紧走过去看发生了什么。
EN: He hurried over to see what happened.

ZH: 我们得尽快赶到机场，否则就要错过飞机了。
EN: We need to hurry to the airport, otherwise we will miss the plane.

ZH: 他不喜欢赶公共汽车，所以经常选择步行。
EN: He doesn't like catching the bus, so he often chooses to walk.

ZH: 昨天我们赶上了最后一班地铁。
EN: Yesterday we caught the last subway.

ZH: 老板让我赶快完成这个任务。
EN: The boss told me to finish this task quickly.

ZH: 孩子们赶着去学校，生怕迟到。
EN: The children hurried to school, afraid of being late.

ZH: 没时间了，我们必须得赶紧离开这里。
EN: There is no time, we must hurry to leave here.

ZH: 我的车突然坏了，我必须叫人来赶修。
EN: My car suddenly broke down, I must call someone to repair it.

ZH: 她拼命地赶着写完了论文。
EN: She worked hard to finish the paper.

ZH: 我们要赶飞机，不能再呆在这儿了。
EN: We have to catch the plane, we can't stay here any longer.

ZH: 他被警察赶了出去。
EN: He was driven out by the police.

ZH: 警察命令路人赶快离开现场。
EN: The police ordered the bystanders to leave quickly.

ZH: 他猛地朝她赶去，想救她一命。
EN: He rushed towards her, trying to save her life.

ZH: 赶紧点，我们赶不及上班了。
EN: Hurry up, we're going to be late for work.

ZH: 老师赶着学生们做完这份作业。
EN: The teacher hurried the students to finish this homework.

ZH: 我们在大雨中赶到了目的地。
EN: We arrived at the destination in heavy rain.

ZH: 我们只有五分钟的时间赶到车站。
EN: We only have five minutes to get to the station.

ZH: 赶紧通知大家，会议要延期。
EN: Quickly inform everyone that the meeting is postponed.

ZH: 他拼命赶着完成这个项目。
EN: He worked hard to finish this project.

ZH: 我们赶在太阳下山之前回到了营地。
EN: We returned to the camp before the sun set.
